snippet.title: They Speak from the Abyss: Zenith - Official Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description: Dive into the strange, unsettling world of They Speak from the Abyss: Zenith, a standalone prequel to They Speak From The Abyss. Travel through the realm of despair and head towards the Zenith point. In the distance lies the mighty mansion Melancholia. Will you only find glory, agony, or freedom?
